setPadValue

public double[] setPadValue(double[] padValue)
Set the pad values for each dimension of a variable. The number of elements in the array must match the number of dimensions and the value of of each element is the pad value for the corresponding dimension.

Parameters:
padValue - an array of pad values.
Returns:
the array of pad values (one per dimension) or null if no pad values have been set.
